{"tid":2267640,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"發射放大鏡上宇宙是利多於弊 你同意嗎？","createTime":"2020-11-02T08:17:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-02T13:56:42.000Z","uid":51346,"like":72,"dislike":50,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"c2e6682585405059d03470377a22c30b0e098d37","tid":2267640,"uid":51346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T08:17:16.000Z","msg":"地球離太陽咁遠 用放大鏡都可以燒著張紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁射啲好大塊嘅放大鏡上宇宙應該可以做到好多嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利：<br />\n1.阻止外星人入侵<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CpwHQGf.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCpwHQGf.gif&h=7db8216b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n將太陽光聚焦落架ufo 整到佢爆炸<br />\n<br />\n2..保護地球後欄<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CsZ2Qw0.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCsZ2Qw0.gif&h=e719a757&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n如果有4塊放大鏡圍同地球一樣圍住太陽轉<br />\n咁佢哋聚焦出嚟嘅光柱就可以護住地球屎忽同側邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n太陽系外嘅入侵者一定要兜路先嚟到 同時人類可以守少幾邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n啲放大鏡可以叫陽衛一 陽衛二<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 防止地球受流星雨攻擊<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PQFdXnn.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPQFdXnn.gif&h=0b2bc950&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n啲隕石一掂到聚焦咗嘅光柱就會頂唔順熔晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n4.解決海平面上升問題<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v3dCEBG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv3dCEBG.jpg&h=32f1c9c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n個放大鏡射返落大海 可以蒸發海水 令海平面下降<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n5.解決人口過多 糧食危機 土地問題<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qBbHQJ1.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqBbHQJ1.gif&h=6a327e72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n輕鬆解決<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n弊：<br />\n諗唔到<br />\n<br />\n結論：<br />\n我都唔明帝國咁辛苦整死星做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j2JZSZ8.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj2JZSZ8.gif&h=a6915c1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n地球高達（浮游炮裝備）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\npost尾彩蛋<br />\n如履薄冰鞋2.0<br />\n<br />\n如履薄煙鞋<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wKnLOxa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwKnLOxa.jpg&h=a5e22aae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鞋身裝有放大鏡 可以聚焦光線 煲滾海水 水蒸氣再托返住個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"757f97f2c6836fc16fe8639e1dab5781c1c5304a","tid":2267640,"uid":51346,"like":27,"dislike":2,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T08:17:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>[quote]越關注<br />\n佢地就越安全<br />\n<br />\n許穎婷套片 cls 未？<br />\n每日Twitter 做左未？<br />\n鏗鏘集《十二》 cls未？<br />\n寫左信比手足未？<br />\nBring them back 打卡未<br />\n在囚手足想登報聲援手足你又知唔知？<br />\n<br />\n你是忘記了<br />\n還是害怕想起來</blockquote>許穎婷段12港人片<br />\nYoutube 得六百幾like?<br />\nFacebook 萬九人睇得個800like?<br />\nTwitter 5000人睇都3300like啦喎？<br />\n反而ig成績最好 7200like<br />\n<blockquote><br />\nYoutube<br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/9kqtFMHPjIs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F9kqtFMHPjIs&d=Vpe8FAkBT2vLq%2FWrgjLHxR1%2FCJV8QLW4B9aSVLpa5FM%3D&h=73b73594\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/9kqtFMHPjIs</a><br />\n\t<br />\nFacebook<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/2317436205144840/posts/2740902359464887/?vh=e&amp;d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F2317436205144840%2Fposts%2F2740902359464887%2F%3Fvh%3De%26d%3Dn&d=Vpe8FAkBT2vLq%2FWrgjLHxR1%2FCJV8QLW4B9aSVLpa5FM%3D&h=2305b099\" data-auto-link